  <body>
    <h2>
      Making a Protein Smoothie
    </h2>
    <h4>
      by Joelle John
    </h4>
    <p>
      I make this smoothie when I wake up and when I come from the gym. The protein smoothie helps me build muscle after I work out.
    </p>
    <h3>
      Ingredients
    </h3>
    <ul>
      <li> 1 banana </li>
      <li> protein powder</li>
      <li> spinach </li>
      <li> dark chocolate</li>
      <li> peanut butter</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>
      What to Do
    </h3>
    <ol>
      <li> Chop up the banana</li>
      <li> Measure out 1 1/2 cup of pwder</li>
      <li> Put ice and water in blender </li>
      <li> Put rest of ingredients in blender</li>
      <li> Turn on blender</li>
      <li> Drink</li>
    </ol>
